<style 
      xmlns="http://purl.org/net/xbiblio/csl"
      class="note"
      version="1.0">
  <info>
    <id />
    <title />
    <updated>2009-08-10T04:49:00+09:00</updated>
  </info>
  <locale xml:lang="en">
    <terms>
      <term name="ibid">id.</term>
    </terms>
  </locale>
  <citation>
    <layout delimiter="; ">
      <choose>
      <if position="first">
        <group delimiter=", ">
          <text variable="title"/>
          <group delimiter=" ">
            <text variable="volume"/>
            <text variable="container-title"/>
            <text variable="page"/>
            <date variable="issued" prefix="(" suffix=")">
              <date-part name="year"/>
            </date>
          </group>
        </group>
      </if>
      <else-if position="ibid-with-locator">
        <text term="ibid" suffix=" at "/>
        <text variable="locator"/>
      </else-if>
      <else-if position="ibid">
        <text term="ibid"/>
      </else-if>
      <else-if position="subsequent">
        <group delimiter=", ">
          <text variable="title"/>
          <group delimiter=" ">
            <text variable="volume"/>
            <text variable="container-title"/>
            <choose>
            <if variable="locator">
              <text variable="locator"/>
            </if>
            <else>
              <text variable="page"/>
            </else>
            </choose>
           </group>
        </group>
      </else-if>
      <else>
        <text value="WTF?"/>
      </else>
      </choose>
    </layout>
  </citation>
</style>
